    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>steaks</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each side</p><p>Once the <strong>steaks</strong> are cooked transfer them to a chopping board, cover with a clean tea towel and leave to rest until later</p>",
